          </p>

          <h2
            class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4"
            style="color: #4a9a95 !important;"
          >
            3. HIPAA Compliance and Business Associate Agreement
          </h2>
          <p>
            For healthcare providers subject to the Health Insurance Portability
            and Accountability Act of 1996 and its implementing regulations
