            settings. You must execute a BAA with us before using our services
            to process, transmit, or store PHI.
          </p>
          <p>You represent and warrant that you will:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 my-4">
            <li>
              Comply with all applicable provisions of HIPAA and other
              healthcare privacy laws
            </li>
            <li>
              Obtain all necessary consents and authorizations from
              clients/patients before entering their information into our
